<figure class="aligncenter size-full"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" width="416" height="612" src="https://codechina.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/V43uF.jpg" alt="" class="wp-image-25171" srcset="https://codechina.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/V43uF.jpg 416w, https://codechina.org/wp-content/uploads/2022/11/V43uF-204x300.jpg 204w" sizes="(max-width: 416px) 100vw, 416px" /><figcaption class="wp-element-caption">彩色兵马俑</figcaption></figure></div>

